MyBroadband is growing its editorial team, and is looking for candidates who can take on the role of Tech Journalist. We are looking for journalists who like technology, gaming, and online news – or techies and gamers who like writing and think they would excel at an online news publication. To ensure we get the best applicants, we are offering a sweet incentive to the person we hire in a permanent position – a gaming PC worth R25,000. This will get you the following rig: For AMD fans, the CPU and GPU can be replaced with AMD components. If you would like to apply for the journalist position at MyBroadband: If you apply for a position and are hired full-time by MyBroadband, the gaming PC – and the best job in tech journalism – is yours.